\/07\/nasihah-ikhlaas-hiqd\/","url_meta":{"origin":37993,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sincerity: Good will protects from hatred, malice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 7, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere are three traits by which a believer will have no malice: sincerity in deeds for Allah, goodwill to the Muslims, and uniting with their community.\" Source: Musnad al-Sha\u0304miyyi\u0304n lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 1279 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi\u00a0(authentic\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20978,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/10\/03\/ali-nasihah-believers-good-will\/","url_meta":{"origin":37993,"position":2},"title":"Ali on Sincerity: Believers have good will, love for each other","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 3, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn 'Asakir reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, the believers are people with good will and love for each other, even if their lands and countries are far apart. The hypocrites are people with malevolence for each other.\u201d Source: Ta\u0304ri\u0304kh Dimashq 23310 \u0639\u0646\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40583,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/04\/islam-is-naseehah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37